# LLM API Gateway — 数据模型与类图

## 1. 数据模型 ER 图

```mermaid
erDiagram
    users ||--|| quotas : "1:1"
    users ||--o{ call_logs : "1:N"
    users ||--o{ admin_sessions : "1:N (Admin only)"

    users {
        int id PK
        string username UK
        string password_hash
        string sub_key_hash UK
        string sub_key_preview
        string role "admin | user"
        string status "active | disabled"
        string created_at
        string updated_at
    }

    quotas {
        int id PK
        int user_id FK_UK
        int quota_5h_limit "默认 1000000"
        int quota_5h_used "每5h重置"
        int quota_total_limit "默认 100000000"
        int quota_total_used "累计不重置"
        string window_start "当前窗口起始"
        string updated_at
    }

    call_logs {
        int id PK
        int user_id FK
        string model "glm-5.2"
        int prompt_tokens
        int completion_tokens
        int total_tokens
        int status_code "200/429/500"
        int latency_ms
        string error_msg
        string created_at
    }

    admin_sessions {
        int id PK
        string session_token UK
        string created_at
        string expires_at "24h"
    }
```

---

## 2. 核心服务类图

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Config {
        +string ListenAddr
        +string DBPath
        +string ZhipuBaseURL
        +int ResetIntervalHours
        +Load(path string) Config
    }

    class DB {
        +*sql.DB Conn
        +Open(path string) DB
        +Migrate()
        +Close()
    }

    class User {
        +int64 ID
        +string Username
        +string PasswordHash
        +string SubKeyHash
        +string SubKeyPreview
        +string Role
        +string Status
        +Create(db, user) error
        +FindBySubKeyHash(db, hash) User
        +List(db) []User
        +Update(db, id, fields) error
    }

    class Quota {
        +int64 ID
        +int64 UserID
        +int Quota5hLimit
        +int Quota5hUsed
        +int QuotaTotalLimit
        +int QuotaTotalUsed
        +string WindowStart
        +FindByUserID(db, userID) Quota
        +AtomicDeduct(db, userID, tokens) bool
        +ResetAll5h(db) error
    }

    class CallLog {
        +int64 ID
        +int64 UserID
        +string Model
        +int TotalTokens
        +int StatusCode
        +int LatencyMs
        +Insert(db, log) error
        +FindByUserID(db, userID, from, to, page, limit) []CallLog
    }

    class AdminSession {
        +int64 ID
        +string SessionToken
        +string ExpiresAt
        +Create(db) AdminSession
        +Validate(db, token) bool
        +Delete(db, token) error
    }

    class AuthMiddleware {
        +AuthenticateSubKey(r *http.Request) (userID, error)
        +AuthenticateAdmin(r *http.Request) bool
    }

    class QuotaChecker {
        +Check(userID, estimatedTokens) (allowed bool, reason string)
        +Deduct(userID, actualTokens) error
    }

    class QuotaScheduler {
        +Start()
        +Reset()
        +Compensate()
    }

    class ProxyHandler {
        +ServeHTTP(w, r)
        -handleSync(w, r, userID)
        -handleStream(w, r, userID)
    }

    class AdminHandler {
        +ServeHTTP(w, r)
        +handleLogin(w, r)
        +handleCreateUser(w, r)
        +handleListUsers(w, r)
        +handleUpdateUser(w, r)
        +handleGetCalls(w, r)
        +handleOverview(w, r)
    }

    class KeyGenerator {
        +GenerateSubKey(userID) string
        +HashKey(subKey) string
    }

    Config --> DB : configures
    AuthMiddleware --> User : queries
    AuthMiddleware --> AdminSession : validates
    QuotaChecker --> Quota : reads/updates
    QuotaScheduler --> Quota : resets
    ProxyHandler --> QuotaChecker : checks
    ProxyHandler --> KeyGenerator : uses
    ProxyHandler --> CallLog : logs
    AdminHandler --> User : manages
    AdminHandler --> Quota : reads
    AdminHandler --> CallLog : queries
    AdminHandler --> AdminSession : manages
    AdminHandler --> KeyGenerator : generates
```

---

## 3. 配额状态机

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Normal : 配额充足

    Normal --> Warn5h : 5h_used >= 80% limit
    Normal --> WarnTotal : total_used >= 80% limit

    Warn5h --> Exhausted5h : 5h_used >= 5h_limit
    Warn5h --> Normal : 窗口重置

    WarnTotal --> ExhaustedTotal : total_used >= total_limit
    WarnTotal --> Normal : Admin 提升配额

    Exhausted5h --> Normal : 窗口重置（自动）
    Exhausted5h --> ExhaustedBoth : total 也耗尽

    ExhaustedTotal --> Normal : Admin 提升配额
    ExhaustedTotal --> ExhaustedBoth : 5h 也耗尽

    ExhaustedBoth --> ExhaustedTotal : 窗口重置
    ExhaustedBoth --> Exhausted5h : Admin 提升总配额
```
